== 制造厂家 ==

*[[印度|印度]]：「Grasim」是世界上最大的生产厂家，占全球份额的24%<ref name="Grasim">{{Cite web |url=http://www.grasim.com/products/birla_viscose.htm |title=Grasim |accessdate=2006-07-19 |archive-date=2006-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060515052913/http://www.grasim.com/products/birla_viscose.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。
*[[奥地利|奥地利]]：Lenzing Fibers Corp.<ref name="Lenzing">{{Cite web |url=http://www.lenzing.com/fibers/en/textiles/4178.jsp |title=Lenzing Fibers |access-date=2006-07-19 |archive-date=2006-09-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060905002232/http://www.lenzing.com/fibers/en/textiles/4178.jsp |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。
*[[德国|德国]]：Kelheim Fibres,<ref name="Kelheim">{{Cite web |url=http://www.kelheim-fibres.com/service/images/viskose.pdf |title=Kelheim Fibres |access-date=2006-07-19 |archive-date=2006-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060620191617/http://kelheim-fibres.com/service/images/viskose.pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。
*[[台湾|台湾]]：[[中國人造纤维工业股份有限公司|中國人造纤维工业股份有限公司]]
*[[美国|美国]]：North American Rayon Corp，已于2000年停产<ref name="Tennessee encyclopedia">{{Cite web |url=http://tennesseeencyclopedia.net/imagegallery.php?EntryID=N046 |title=Tennessee Encyclopedia |access-date=2006-07-19 |archive-date=2007-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927190935/http://tennesseeencyclopedia.net/imagegallery.php?EntryID=N046 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
* ''Acordis''，在欧洲、美国、巴西等地有工厂<ref name="Acordis">{{Cite web |url=http://www.fibre2fashion.com/Acordis/ |title=Acordis |access-date=2006-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070708050512/http://www.fibre2fashion.com/Acordis/ |archive-date=2007-07-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

== 用途 ==
用于服装、室内装饰（例如床罩、毯子）。工业上用它来制造手术器械、[[不織布|无纺产品]]、女性卫生用品、[[轮胎|轮胎]]內的[[帘布|帘布]]等。

